    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is acknowledged; the single-configuration limitation is considered acceptable given the regulatory precedent for ASTM F1717 as a standalone submission benchmark and the conservative nature of the compression-bending loading mode. All QoI comparisons pass the pre-established acceptance bounds. The model is accepted for the stated COU.",
